					<span lang="y" class="ml-6">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center align_end">
					<div class="img_area">
						<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_04_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
					</div>
					<div class="text_area">
						<div class="text_row" lang="y">(지름) = (원주)÷(원주율)</div>
						<div class="text_row">
